autocomplete.description:
Answers to the deposit invoice template's `autocomplete_template` questionnaire, used for displaying dynamic answers in the document, the deposit invoice template ID can be found via `clinic_document_template_list?master={invoice_template_id}`, the questionnaire must be retrieved via `document_template_retrieve`

**Questions structure:**

*NOTE: It may contain other irrelevant fields in each object in the "q" array, "h" object may not be present.*

```json
{
  "h": {"val": "optional header text displayed before questions"},
  "q": [
    {
      "id": "type 1 question ID",
      "val": "question text, requires free text answer (type 1, string/textarea)",
      "type": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "type 2 question ID",
      "val": "question text, requires yes/no answer (type 2, bool/checkbox)",
      "type": 2,
      "y": "text next to yes button",
      "n": "text next to no button"
    },
    {
      "id": "type 3 question ID",
      "val": "question text, requires single choice answer (type 3, radio buttons)",
      "type": 3,
      "boxes": [{"id": "radio button ID", "val": "choice text"}, ...]
    },
    {
      "id": "type 4 question ID",
      "val": "question text, requires multiple choice answer (type 4, checkboxes)",
      "type": 4,
      "boxes": [{"id": "checkbox ID", "val": "choice text"}, ...]
    },
    {
      "id": "type 5 question ID",
      "val": "question text, requires integer answer (type 5, scale from 0 to 10)",
      "type": 5,
      "min": 0,
      "max": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "type 6 question ID',
      "val": "question label, requires image answer (type 6, base64 image)",
      "type": 6
    },
    {
      "id": "type 7 question ID",
      "val": "question text, requires date(YYYY-MM-DD)/datetime(ISO 8601) answer (type 7, datepicker)",
      "type": 7
    }
  ]
}
```

**Answers structure:**

```json
{
  "a": [
    {"q_id": "type 1 question ID", "val": "answer to this question"},
    {"q_id": "type 2 question ID", "val": true},
    {"q_id": "type 3 question ID", "val": "radio button ID"},
    {"q_id": "type 4 question ID", "val": ["checkbox ID", ...]},
    {"q_id": "type 5 question ID", "val": 0},
    {"q_id": "type 6 question ID", "val": "data:image/jpeg;base64,..."},
    {"q_id": "type 7 question ID", "val": "2025-06-05"},
  ]
}

```

